overview: A beautiful but awkward teen, Amira is in undergrad studying psychology, while experiencing symptoms of something that she cannot explain. After meeting a cunning guy named Damon, Amira starts to experience abilities that she never knew she had. Mental health or medium - She was struggling to find her identity and way in the world. Seeing spirits, reading minds, and predicting the future were abilities that Amira dreaded having, until she had to use them to try to save her friend Tracey; after she was kidnapped - Amira learns that nothing is as it appears in this life and that perception is the key to everyone's overall well-being.
title: 5D Love
